&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1081&quot; data-end=&quot;1742&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1081&quot; data-end=&quot;1219&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1083&quot; data-end=&quot;1219&quot;&gt;3+ years of experience in construction project management with a thorough understanding of the building design and construction process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1220&quot; data-end=&quot;1309&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1222&quot; data-end=&quot;1309&quot;&gt;Bachelor’s, Associate’s, or equivalent experience in a construction-related discipline.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1310&quot; data-end=&quot;1425&quot;&gt;
